SourceFile: The source file to import (path relative to the json script)
PipelineStack: The pipeline stack to use when importing (an empty array will use the defaults)
bEmptyDestinationFolderPriorToImport: Whether the destination folder should be emptied prior to import
bSaveThenReloadImportedAssets: Whether imported assets should be saved and freshly reloaded after import
bImportIntoLevel: Whether we should use the import into level workflow
